{
  "texts": [
    "The popularity of ML is seeing meteoric growth.",
    "Introductory steps for employing machine learning to diagnose lung diseasesML has the potential to diagnose and prognosticate lung illnesses.",
    "To make a diagnosis using imaging modalities, ML executes a series of actions, including acquiring an image dataset, preprocessing the image data contained within the dataset, performing feature extraction and selection, training an ML model using specific ML algorithms, and evaluating performance metrics and classification [96].",
    "The lung disease diagnostic process using ML is shown in Fig. 11.The above-described introductory steps for employing ML to diagnose lung diseases act as the training phase of the ML model, which develops an ML diagnostic model.",
    "However, this ML diagnostic model must be validated using new or test data that the model has never seen before."
  ]
}